E-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.07;\" id=\"SE-f5528a2c-4b5a-4566-b31e-5de0f5b103ef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7d350e5a-d7ad-4b75-859d-8c6350646990\">혈압과 혈류역학, 열생산, 일부 면역기능 등 다양한 기능을 조절함으로써 항</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.07;\" id=\"SE-202cf561-27f6-4043-9f5d-8c6e6c0d17ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6e96654a-7ed3-4940-a407-19a3497afe76\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.07;\" id=\"SE-999335a6-03ae-4be5-9303-ba4e2f5fc527\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1a9d1de0-0c6f-4c9e-b7a9-587790c2ab39\">상성을 유지하는데에 카테콜아민(에피네프린, 노르에피네프린 등 - 교감신</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.07;\" id=\"SE-661d6b29-1f28-48cb-8be5-ff2a31a15db3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d5e0f320-f1e8-46ef-83c9-0172c1968697\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"line-height:1.07;\" id=\"SE-eadb3963-23ff-49ba-879e-17541a125b39\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e492f7eb-2de6-4d0a-9bb4-6e5ee427f22d\">경이 분비하는 신경전달물질이)이 역할을 한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6d25195-047c-49fb-98f7-535110d91592\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c6d25195-047c-49fb-98f7-535110d91592\", \"src\" : \"https://cdn.britannica.com/28/55028-004-BBF22B4C/animals-humans-autonomic-nervous-system-heat-production.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"800\", \"originalHeight\" : \"620\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://cdn.britannica.com/28/55028-004-BBF22B4C/animals-humans-autonomic-nervous-system-heat-production.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-150cc048-4c00-4744-b1d8-7da43c2fb1c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8d5bc45d-d1b8-4650-a9af-358bd3e0efe5\">from - </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-62c078a5-078f-44cc-8484-c7725f622133\"><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/science/autonomic-nervous-system\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.britannica.com/science/autonomic-nervous-system</a></span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96a4ea6b-84b2-4329-a740-f3479db57040\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e055d3e8-8531-4ef7-a687-c5b57a9cbe75\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d19fb04a-edf6-4731-8b28-1f729d6fd8b0\">항상성상태가 교란되면 교감신경계와 시상하부-뇌하수체-부신(HPA axis) 축 계통이 활성화되고 항상성을 회복하려 시도하면서 전신(부신 adrenal)과 말초(신경절이후 요소)의 카테콜아민과 글루코코르티코이드 농도를 상승시킨다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b6f5933-0e9b-40d7-8cbd-0dc054e47ea0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2b6f5933-0e9b-40d7-8cbd-0dc054e47ea0\", \"src\" : \"https://biologydictionary.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/stressresponseactivation.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"576\", \"originalHeight\" : \"500\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://biologydictionary.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/stressresponseactivation.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f18e2a67-d227-438f-b3f9-f9470c0cb7a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d83b879a-87c3-4e3d-b37b-329d1f9da5dd\">from - </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4315c98f-7370-4d26-b4fc-790ef104733f\"><a href=\"https://biologydictionary.net/hpa-axis/\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://biologydictionary.net/hpa-axis/</a></span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c9ac9b00-e318-47db-a3f1-65dc8fcb2435\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f04f5bdd-d84a-48ad-9a95-bbe0a611b053\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-33f3d6dc-ef6f-47e3-9f42-e67982f04f83\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ee1541c5-6dc6-4d3f-be50-2f01d225e6b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dbaa869d-bef3-416e-be3f-2ade258a8d46\">참고 – General adaptation syndrome (Hans selye) : 한스 셀리에가 정립한 인체가 항상성을 깨뜨리는 외부 스트레스에 어떻게 반응하는지에 대한 이론. 스트레스에 대한 교감신경성, adrenal 성 반응들이 위궤양, 흉선위축, 부신(adrenal)비대 등의 결과를 불러온다는 이론. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6388d5b5-2e38-4ff9-97ab-b3d04728edf1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-6388d5b5-2e38-4ff9-97ab-b3d04728edf1\", \"src\" : \"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/General_Adaptation_Syndrome.jpg/600px-General_Adaptation_Syndrome.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"438\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/General_Adaptation_Syndrome.jpg/600px-General_Adaptation_Syndrome.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7958ec7f-e809-43fd-9257-d5d0b6af730b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b2c3abbb-603d-49bd-bc2b-6c9edee06743\"><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%ED%95%9C%EC%8A%A4_%EC%85%80%EB%A6%AC%EC%97%90\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\"><b>한스 셀리에</b></a></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a59f2ce5-37f1-40d2-831d-2dbb82438e36\"><b>(Hans Selye)는 </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1c6d00cc-7c55-4c68-a18d-8c5f6bb7bf40\"><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%8A%A4\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\"><b>스트레스</b></a></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6f557911-4bee-4c6d-a65b-cc460f4d473d\"><b>에대해서 일반 적응 증후군(General Adaptation Syndrome; GAS)를 언급한 바 있다. 여기서 일반(General)이란 스트레스는 생물체의 행동인 &#x27;생존과 번식&#x27;과 관련하여 광범위하고 일반적인 과정하에 놓여있다는 의미이며 적응(Adaptation)이란 스트레스 원인으로부터 신체가 이를 대처하게 하거나 수용하려한다는 의미이며, </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-35ec2da8-3530-466b-8130-799d2f0ec910\"><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%A6%9D%ED%9B%84\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\"><b>증후</b></a></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5ed66269-3072-4209-b0a4-9c20f382be03\"><b>(Syndrome)란 스트레스 결과에 의거해 어떤 반응이 일어난다는 의미이다.</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-067ee6bf-5bfa-4690-a1ae-554366996769\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c64caa37-d3f2-44ca-9250-416644b98302\"><b>스트레스를 경험하면 인체는 생리상 정상수준을 유지하고자 스트레스에 경계(alarm)하거나 스트레스에 저항(resistance)한다. 스트레스는 스트레스 자극에 반응해 평온한 상태(homeostasis)를 유지하려는 생리상 반응, 즉 ‘</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f2355517-37fe-4857-b189-5aa548040389\"><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%8B%B8%EC%9B%80-%EB%8F%84%EC%A3%BC_%EB%B0%98%EC%9D%91\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\"><b>싸움-도주 반응</b></a></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85b3c0f0-708b-4991-9b2e-b9acb041bdc3\"><b>(fight or flight)’의 과정이다.</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5c97a61e-9a78-4827-a147-2c7228720822\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6b201ace-8ebb-4985-9020-4a7a78c9cbe6\"><b>여기서 주요한 현상은 탈진(exhaustion)이다. 탈진은 스트레스에대한 일반적인 과정인 경계(또는 경보)나 저항 보다도 더 광범위하고 지속적인 스트레스 상황에 장시간 노출됨으로써 신체적 에너지 고갈을 야기할뿐만아니라 심리적으로 정서적인 불안정한 상태에 취약하게 만들수있다는 점에서 매우 위협적이다. - from wiki -</b></span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-923d7137-23fe-4e30-ac6a-351105694eee\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-864340fb-9d83-46fd-9900-ae393269ef9e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fc611b8a-5b0e-43a3-80eb-e1acea0be79a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d4219fd4-5a5d-4895-90ed-c430fec85e2a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6b6a885b-1b2e-4ef9-8e28-40319704e7b9\">시상하부 뇌실곁핵에서 생산되는 부신겉질자극호르몬(ACTH) 분비호르몬의 생산과 분비 + 뇌줄기 청색반점 노르에피네프린 분비계통으로부터의 노르에피네프린 분비량 증가. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-08518f7c-a843-4753-999e-d5283bea402e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e098555a-ca4d-44fb-95d1-ffa0a3c47689\">-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b31f0550-2460-4581-9371-20fb7fcb3527\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a029dd30-ebfa-45bb-aada-75372e09b91c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-beca8475-18e7-449d-86d6-2d03d9e078cf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dbb96392-694a-423e-84b3-d0554c2d01f8\">즉,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7439f3ff-0f26-433c-ac26-2fb5fe27eed8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-38cb281a-7e12-4492-ba6b-f81b5e4bdf16\">자율신경계는 인체의 항상성을 유지한다. 우리의 의지와 무관하게, &#x27;자율적으로&#x27; 말이다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1123c525-0862-41dd-b0af-cf7c934be5bc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4213acb5-56a2-4bc3-a472-2c9a9548a857\">체온이 낮아지면 체온을 올리고, 혈압이 떨어지면 혈압을 높이고, 혈액순환이 안되면 혈액순환을 개선해주는 등.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-427ce368-99fd-4a01-be9c-2d6bea5a3cfc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-05a17d76-cca5-4392-8838-7bdac49e8a2b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b16327f2-5653-4412-b767-c1e4f8637787\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-06708964-35dd-4cc8-a667-92ebdffaf937\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-16f5f2bd-7a71-4055-af5a-8955a48246d9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dbe30fb4-ebde-4042-8963-398d26bc11c5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85926c9e-276b-4d32-9b19-3a79178e1c93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fb4c9677-f168-4be6-ab06-0e649860d6ff\">자율신경계는 교감신경과 부교감신경으로 구분이 되고, 이 둘은 서로 반대되는 작용을 통해 길항관계에 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-901dbfce-7504-489e-bf11-223ca601a5d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7ab7bf5a-ad77-42f2-a25a-3e14f3c58889\">교감, 부교감 신경이 작용할때 신체에서 어떤 일들이 벌어지는지는 아래 표를 보면 확인할 수 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-108af585-9a13-4190-abf0-fe875318d449\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f1f75518-deea-4d99-93f8-0986883eff97\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-88ff7b6b-5877-4294-8fd4-920b4d8364fe\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n                            <div class=\"se-table-container\">\n                                <table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n                                    <tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-164545b0-dcc3-4938-b36e-b25bb582f03a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1e91b48c-5f5e-415b-a916-5edd80c49701\">교감신경</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-554f82a1-decf-44f0-b11d-6290ad5b39e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-51a1c204-0cee-49fb-803a-11b56e5842d2\">부교감신경</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-6162824c-a316-4268-a44f-58683cee25cf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7b899692-2e3d-4f76-9bfb-7bea469d3c42\">방광 속조임근(internal sphincter) 수축, 배뇨근(detrusor) 억제  - 배뇨를 참아</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-953aa067-85ff-4e50-8dbe-c25e38e8b32a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ade858af-3a37-43e9-af1c-797453da6ff2\">배뇨근 흥분, 속조임근 억제</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-e39d8e35-0db8-4395-aa20-61bd99d60637\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6bf51f4f-dbb9-4113-aae3-d24cb6422a26\">-       배뇨를 진행 (바깥 조임근은 수의 조절)</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-0fbb997a-608e-45a4-8c9b-0fc91607f4ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c86173d-6b3d-4c6f-aa7f-a7e13c8087d7\">콩팥 동백 수축</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-ebcea9a2-b441-4b00-881a-9f3fd651129c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e9f38397-ec07-4155-903d-048568576d42\">콩팥 동맥 확장</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-1a1675e3-fffa-43b5-b203-0ca2109ffaef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-702d7dcf-2fe2-4851-9161-18a79b8aad5f\">부신 속질에서 노르에피네프린, 에피네프린(1:4) 등 카테콜아민의 생산 분비가 증가</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-2923c6c5-5df9-48e1-bd19-823ce677ddab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1097122b-6761-49fa-b276-01c60dcfb3dc\"> </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-2450ef99-f8fd-4581-bf5e-f40f7e0d297a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8b073e3b-b868-4ed8-a10e-e73cf294058d\">안구 세동맥의 혈관 수축 정도를 제어</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-1d2c7172-7c06-41bd-a913-d5e45544a3fc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e3e1cc3f-eefb-48c7-bf24-2b38377a0fc5\">동공이 확대. 모양체근. 수청체 </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-a36435a7-9dd5-4382-bdd8-8562d002aaca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6e249c67-b9ba-4d3d-aff0-6ba65bfae296\">섬모체근(ciliary m.) -수정체, 동공조임근(sphincter pupillae) </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-ec9ea8ea-e1e7-4a37-97be-44b269e6a9c0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-05d34dfe-eb30-4783-b2e2-1be7326e6e55\">위눈꺼풀올림근 수축</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-919f9870-e8cc-42bd-b7b2-a4b475949687\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-26a2a1a4-52ec-4ac7-850f-910adc9c66b8\">턱밑샘 샘 세동맥 확장, 침 생산 증가</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-f5a474d9-2385-4bf9-a48a-e0f36507faab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-666ea291-4ee9-48a8-aa11-4d2b067a9cd6\">귀밑샘 샘 세동맥 확장, 침 생산 증가</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 4.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-16fdb1c1-8f77-44f1-be9e-24ff372fd4fa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39cbda3c-2513-4c65-aacf-7689cf3d3f12\">Vestibuloautonomic reflexes를 통해 자세를 바꿀 때 혈관운동 긴장도를 조절. </span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-5302348e-3085-4181-ab2c-214520a20510\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ac1fe017-6baf-4d65-a523-f3662dc5a961\">-&gt;기립성 저혈압을 방지.</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-3b3c1051-00ae-453b-b63d-16c42f4dde7a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-eb3875a3-dd3f-4fc3-a617-599974c3c215\">안뜰계통이 과활성을 보이면 목동맥나무 전반에 걸친 혈관운동 긴장도 항진이 과다해서 어지럼증이 생길 수 있다.</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 4.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-5f29bf64-7ffd-43c6-873a-ddccbdb8e69c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-829e7ca7-c16b-47d5-9dae-8a6461b5ac66\">Vagus n. 운동 투사섬유는 숨뇌 ambiguous nucleus와 dorsal motor nucleus 에서 시작. 심장은 억제- 심박 느리게, 기관지 민무늬근육 수축-기관지 수축, 위샘 자극하고 날문조임근 억제, 장관으로는 샘과 근육에 대한 흥분신호 전달, 회맹괄약근에는 억제신호 전달. </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-20d0f3cd-95fe-458e-9348-d5184efd6fa1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0dbabfc-8b09-4f94-8076-c273833bd2cf\">말초신경 근육의 혈관에만 신경지배. 혈관의 혈관수축근 신경섬유.  활성화- 혈관수축</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-8c378bb3-db0e-4898-98e9-3a0b4e275de5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e8d9297a-38f6-4a8e-9aaf-42f3b83ead42\"> </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-35e8021b-6145-4884-a115-35a6b4098e34\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2ef96646-5bd9-4fef-8915-e6c201f4bf7b\">털세움근 활성화</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-0865931e-797c-4323-bb02-18dba33a4c26\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9807d982-8e31-4d34-972b-cc3c320f16f8\"> </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-1419851f-2ae4-4e9b-ac34-cf7bdeab2808\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d5d90eac-c9b7-4255-a2a7-ad54e4f897cb\">땀샘에 대한 분비촉진</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-8183bdc6-ea21-4492-9f76-d03848ef40be\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c977a6c7-237e-45a6-aa1d-c7883343aebf\"> </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-d596582b-7da7-4852-81cd-6dd0e210fbaa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-56c5ad99-bf10-4321-927e-76e98cbb6c83\">T1 IML-&gt;superior cervical ganglion-&gt;internal carotid nerve-&gt;두개골 내부 진입-&gt;carotid plexus형성-&gt;모든 뇌신경을 따라 진행-&gt;뇌신경 분포부위의 혈관에 신경지배</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-3b653df3-934e-4b63-aeb4-f2f33977008d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6ddb7adc-6cef-4133-8810-9325ac70f92f\"> </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-d5c868d6-ce80-4976-8a64-83bb84209e06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3b76dd48-7926-4667-bf76-ad2d3bba99e2\">T2~5 척추옆신경절에서 출발 - 허파에서 기관지와 혈관이 모두 확장</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 3.8000000000000003px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-46c21c07-acc4-4293-bb80-d8b759627410\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7069ff6e-917a-4ef0-a116-07f5d574a0f8\">DMN에서 출발 – 기관지 혈관 수축. 샌 분비물 생산 증가</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-7a094229-1ae5-4373-aa2f-642c98be6050\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0215640b-f9bc-403d-a265-96663c698c30\">L1-2 회색질 -&gt; lumbar plexus -&gt; hypogastric plexus -&gt; 정관, 정낭, 전립샘의 민무늬근의 수축 -&gt; 사정</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-beaaf9e2-8e36-4cc0-a79e-a3d8c005eb37\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e3a99098-0c5e-42ed-968e-74083a0e5359\">S1~4 -&gt; hypogastric plexus -&gt; 음경과 음핵에 충혈 – 발기. </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-628b7529-d0d8-4da4-ac77-9f947d67666a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3a4ecc0d-3cc1-4aa6-9bdf-d5ed9dcf1843\">T12~L1- Hypogastric P -&gt; 자궁 혈관수축, 자궁 민무늬근 수축.</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-e2cd3dbe-24ee-402a-98c0-b6028806f7c5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fdeabe17-84d3-4ee2-bab6-ff1ceaca35cc\">S2-4 -  자궁근육 이완, 혈관 확장.</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-5bf16ef3-cdbd-4d7c-88cc-d441915bfc2e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-93216263-ea0a-4e25-a8f4-e74d88e4dae6\">교감신경 항진 쪽 이마 피부온도 저하</span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 50.0%; height: 40.0px; border-top:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left:none;border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext; \">\n\n                                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.3;\" id=\"SE-d64b82ba-db94-4666-b015-3dca94704f7c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-40d11957-c22e-424b-acca-855b7a87a47b\"> </span></p></div>\n                \n                                    </td></tr></tbody>\n                                </table>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_table\", \"id\" : \"SE-88ff7b6b-5877-4294-8fd4-920b4d8364fe\", \"data\": { \"columnCount\" : \"2\" }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ab10ebd3-5b54-4a54-acfc-55e931ebc3b7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fc025002-c8c8-4695-9ee5-93fd0b74e5db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c6a8b66-fdae-43ed-b2a0-4ff952db1a7c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b367e653-59b0-4130-a999-ddf893c3fd12\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-db3ac5af-d379-43c3-960d-9b9d075167ef\">자세변화에 따른 혈압의 변화를 조절하는 것도 자율신경이다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0d661f2d-8b7b-4f7e-bde0-057b9e8d662b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f922b2e8-edb3-4e38-8b87-ee09ece1c112\">누워있을 때는 뇌와 심장이 같은 높이에 있어  심장에서 뇌로 쉽게 혈액이 흘러가기 때문에 심장박출이 강하지 않아도 된다. 그러나 누워있다가 빠르게 일어서면 갑자기 뇌가 심장보다 높이 위치하기 때문에  심장에서 더 강한 힘으로 혈액을 뿜어줘야 뇌까지 도달할 수 있게된다. 이러한 자세변화에 따른 심박출과 혈액순환의 조절이 자율신경에 의해 조절되는데, 이 기능이 제대로 되지 못하면 앉거나 누워있는 자세에서 갑자기 일어날때, 뇌에 일시적으로 혈액이 부족해지면서 &#x27;기립성 저혈압&#x27; 증상이 발생하고 어지러움, 창백함, 식은땀, 탈력감 등을 경험하고 심하면 혼절하는 경우도 생기게 된다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4de1b5b-92b2-486f-869c-a17aba6956aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bfda1041-0703-4a01-af03-30ea2a2c6eba\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-067dacb9-6969-4e37-91cb-fda410fee6e2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-28b1f8d1-1ec2-4e22-87d6-f7007c04a455\">자율신경계의 기능이 적절하게 잘 유지되야 건강할 수 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
